      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AbstractMeanVarianceEstimator<D extends Distribution>
      Estimators that work on Mean and Variance only (i.e. the first two moments only).
      class  ExponentialMOMEstimator
      Estimate Exponential distribution parameters using the mean, which is the maximum-likelihood estimate (MLE), but not very robust.

      Simple parameter estimation for the Gamma distribution.
      class  NormalMOMEstimator
      Naive maximum-likelihood estimations for the normal distribution using mean and sample variance.

      Estimate parameter of the Wald distribution.
